title: Handy Lyrics The Story So Far
creator: Kultida Anekboon

extendedInfo.description: If you are The Story So Far's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check The Story So Far's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all The Story So Far's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of The Story So Far's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)************************Main Features ************************- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics************************List of albums ************************- Under Soil And Dirt- What You Don't See************************List of lyrics ************************- All Wrong- Bad Luck- Closure- Daughters- Empty Space- Face Value- Four Years- Framework- High Regard- May- Mt. Diablo- Placeholder- Playing The Victim- Quicksand- Rally Cap- Right Here- Roam- Small Talk- States And Minds- Stifled- Swords And Pens- The Glass- Things I Can't Change
